"the lines wrap in the composer window. Having word wrapping disabled in the "
"Options menu isn't enough. Thus, if your patch has very long lines, you must "
"make the composer window very wide before sending the email. See: https://"
"bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=174034"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../process/email-clients.rst:152
msgid ""
